conversation_summary:
Dew-cooled lawn, fairy lights in Jess’s hair, red cup warm against palm.  
Black bike ticks, headless rider carries looping chest-bomb; key brands fence-scar.  
Up-side-down tables float like burning kites; Jess’s glitter palm offers soot-smile fate-swap.  
Mattress-thick fog swallows beam; filmstrip ankle-tether hums 24 blank frames.  
Projector idles in dark soundstage, one taped X, star rigged from seat-vinyl; breath is raw stock, undeveloped.
